  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/d0ef96f6147b80aa93f6b12c3adb2422.avif?t=1771423537\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/a3beaaeaa2772d53bfa0b269bc3603bb.poster.avif?t=1771423537\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/a3beaaeaa2772d53bfa0b269bc3603bb.webm?t=1771423537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/a3beaaeaa2772d53bfa0b269bc3603bb.mp4?t=1771423537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CRAZY SYNERGIES</strong> with over 100 upgrades that affect your run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/132d9aec45d2801b5815a95b4170accb.avif?t=1771423537\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Swing your <strong>PHYSICS-BASED</strong> fishing line, cast your lure and hope for a bite! <strong>OVER 200 DIFFERENT FISH!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/a91778ca9e3e2b3560a2a9bed3acb34d.poster.avif?t=1771423537\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/a91778ca9e3e2b3560a2a9bed3acb34d.webm?t=1771423537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/a91778ca9e3e2b3560a2a9bed3acb34d.mp4?t=1771423537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808320/extras/e9f5f85fadd05be8ce430bcaf4e9b638.avif?t=1771423537\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Make interesting decisions with <strong>RANDOMLY PLACED PUZZLES</strong> that affect the entire lake!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">AND MORE:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tons of REPLAYABILITY:</strong>  <br>Different lakes, treasures, puzzles, and enemy encounters each playthrough!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Build VARIETY:</strong><br>COMBINE UPGRADES to find CRAZY ATTACK SYNERGIES!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>STUFF TO UNLOCK:</strong><br>Unlock new characters, treasures and features by completing additional quests!</p>",
